title: France's Reunion Island prepares for tropical storm Berguitta
text:
France's Reunion Island prepares for tropical storm Berguitta 3:32pm IST - 00:49 
Residents of the French overseas island of Reunion prepare for tropical storm Berguitta carrying winds of up to 170km/hr (105 miles/hr) . Rough cut (no reporter narration).
